# Rust
target/
# Cargo.lock is committed for both binary crates (R1 — funding-readiness):
# reproducible benchmarks require pinned dependency versions. Library
# crates would still gitignore Cargo.lock; both Rust crates here are
# binaries (zk_ml_prover, zk_compile_prover).

